          <text><![CDATA[<p> <b>Promoting Quality of Care in Pain Management Act of 2018</b></p> <p>This bill requires the Centers for Medicare &amp; Medicaid Services to convene a technical expert panel to recommend opioid and opioid-use disorder quality measures for possible use in hospital payment and reporting models under Medicare.</p>]]></text>
